                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> Written in the main hand. The note mentions šum ʾAgame Gabra
                              Ḫǝywät as the commissioner and ʾAśrāta Māryām as the scribe. Besides,
                              his wife Maḫḍäntä Māryām, his father Nǝblä Dǝngǝl, his mother ʾArsema,
                              and his children Walda Giyorgis, Walda Mikāʾel, qes Walda ʾAragāwi,
                              qes Zarʾa Yoḥannǝs, Za-Śǝllāse, Walda Yoḥannǝs, Takla Yoḥannǝs,
                              Walatta Mikāʾel are mentioned. </note>
